<p>More importantly, the team lead no longer needs to be a "firefighter" and can focus on campaign strategy optimization.</p>
<h2>Does Your Team Need Kanban?</h2>
<p>If your team meets any of these conditions, kanban management is essential:</p>
<ul>
<li>Managing 3+ ad platforms</li>
<li>Working with 2+ agencies simultaneously</li>
<li>Handling 10+ monthly account tasks</li>
<li>Having experienced campaign disruptions due to unclear account status</li>
</ul>
<p>Agency account management isn't a one-time action—it's continuous operations. Use kanban to document each account's complete lifecycle, and efficiency improvements will become immediately apparent.</p>
